@apiUrl =  https://fw-teaching.fi/demo/wdbocms/api/v1/products/


###Get all products

GET {{apiUrl}}

###Get one product

GET {{apiUrl}}/1001

### Create new product
POST {{apiUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name" : "Jeans",
  "price" : 49
}



### Update Product info
PATCH {{apiUrl}}/1001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name" : "Jeans",
  "price" : 29
}



###Delete product
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/1004